  "vulnerability_information": "When the ldap server is (temporarily) unavailable, data like the attached ends up in log files. I've replaced usernames with `XXX_USERn_XXX` and passwords with `XXX_PASSn_XXX`. It seems that at least the following are missing from `$methodsWithSensitiveParameters` in `lib/private/Log.php`:\n - `bind`\n - `areCredentialsValid`\n - `invokeLDAPMethod`\n - `checkPasswordNoLogging`",
